<!-- Quick Steps -->

|**Phase**|**Description**|**Steps**|
|:--------|:--------------|:--------|
|Define/Discover|Requirements, success, risks for your migration project.|1.	Download MAP Toolkit from Microsoft Download Center.
2. Get reports on Discovery & Inventory, Oracle schema reporting, and Hardware and Platform details.|
|Assessment|Inventory of your current database assets and application stack discovery.|1.	Download SQL Server Migration Assistant from Microsoft Download Center.
2. Review database objects and data
3. Assess databases for migration.|
|Migration & Remediation|Schema and data migration; perform validations. |1. Download SQL Server Migration Assistant from Microsoft Download Center.
2. Review database objects and data
3. Migrate Oracle databases to SQL Server or Azure SQL Database.|
|Optimization|Fix performance issues with the workload.|TBD|


